## <a id='features'></a>Key Features

Boomi AtomSphere Integration Services for PCF includes the following key features:

* Trivial Provisioning: Developers can easily provision one or more Boomi Atoms.
  The Atom's VM and file-system sizes can be configured using the standard PCF mechanisms.
* Runtime Isolation: Each Boomi Atom runs within its own dedicated VM within PCF, providing individual, isolated integration runtime environments.
* Integrated Management: The Boomi Atom service is managed entirely by the PCF service life cycle.

