## <a id="reqs"></a>Requirements

Boomi AtomSphere Integration Services for PCF has the following requirements:

+ The ability to deploy a Boomi Atom on PCF requires a Boomi AtomSphere license. If you are not currently a Boomi
customer, you can get a [30-day free trial](https://marketing.boomi.com/trial).
+ Boomi Atoms must be able to connect to the Boomi AtomSphere platform.
  The **Internet Connected** option must always be enabled for the Atom VMs.
  If there is an outbound firewall in place, certain hostnames must be accessible.
  For the complete list of hostnames, see the row titled "Install and maintain Atoms, Molecules or Atom Clouds"
  in [Hostnames and IP addresses for connecting with Dell Boomi](http://help.boomi.com/atomsphere/GUID-18185BA9-A157-4B2E-B426-FE340D02C986.html).

